001package io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.storage;
002
003import lombok.Getter;
004
005/**
006 * Defines keys used for storing and retrieving global test execution data.
007 *
008 * <p>This enum provides unique identifiers for managing test execution contexts,
009 * metadata, and framework-level consumers within the storage system.
010 *
011 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
012 */
013@Getter
014public enum StoreKeys {
015
016   /**
017    * Key for storing the current {@code SuperQuest} instance.
018    */
019   QUEST,
020
021   /**
022    * Key for storing a list of consumers that modify or interact with the quest instance.
023    */
024   QUEST_CONSUMERS,
025
026   /**
027    * Key for storing the start time of the test execution.
028    */
029   START_TIME,
030
031   /**
032    * Key for storing the rendered HTML output or fragments for use in reporting or visualization.
033    */
034   HTML,
035
036   /**
037    * Key for storing hook-related parameters, such as setup and teardown data,
038    * to be shared between extensions and test logic.
039    */
040   HOOKS_PARAMS;
041
042}
